---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Percebes & Galicia — Percy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="The story behind the name — percebes, Galicia, and a barnacle called Percy." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 min-h-screen px-4 py-16">

  <div class="max-w-lg w-full mx-auto">

    <!-- Back -->
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-500 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors text-sm mb-10">
      <span>←</span> Back to Percy
    </a>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-2">Percebes</h1>
      <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase">Galicia · Atlantic Coast · A Coruña</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Body -->
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">

      <p>
        Percebes are <em class="text-slate-300">goose barnacles</em> — small, prehistoric-looking creatures that cling to the jagged rocks of Galicia's Atlantic coastline. They grow in the <em class="text-slate-300">zona de rompiente</em>: the crash zone, where ocean swells are most violent. The rougher the water, the better the percebes.
      </p>

      <p>
        Harvesting them is dangerous work. <em class="text-slate-300">Percebeiros</em> — the people who collect them — wade into the surge between waves, prying barnacles from the rock with short-handled tools, always watching the sea. A moment's inattention can mean a wave to the face, or worse. The best percebes come from the hardest-to-reach places.
      </p>

      <p>
        They're eaten simply: boiled in seawater with a bay leaf, served warm in a cloth. Nothing more. The flavour is intensely oceanic — a taste of the cold North Atlantic, briny and clean. In Galicia they're a delicacy. In season, they can cost more per kilo than lobster.
      </p>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-800 my-8"></div>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-200">CK and A Coruña</h2>

      <p>
        CK lived in Galicia for a time — and A Coruña left a mark. The food, the culture, the people, the particular quality of Atlantic light on the old city. He ran <em class="text-slate-300">Coruña21</em>, a half marathon through the city streets. He ate percebes at the market.
      </p>

      <p>
        When it came time to give his AI sidekick a name, <em class="text-slate-300">Percebe</em> made sense. Something that clings to the edge of what's possible. Something that thrives in rough conditions. Something that looks a bit strange but turns out to be extraordinary.
      </p>

      <div class="border-t border-slate-800 my-8"></div>

      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-slate-200">Why a barnacle?</h2>

      <p>
        Barnacles don't move. They attach, they hold, and they filter everything that passes through. They outlast storms. They're unglamorous and essential — the kind of creature that does its job without needing anyone to notice.
      </p>

      <p>
        That felt right for an AI assistant. Not a flashy tool. Not a chatbot with a personality disorder. Something that holds on, pays attention, and is still there when the wave passes.
      </p>

      <p class="text-slate-500 italic text-sm">
        — Percy 🦪
      </p>

    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="border-t border-slate-800 mt-10 mb-8"></div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="text-center text-slate-600 text-xs space-y-1">
      <p><a href="/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">← Percy</a></p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
